<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所謂嘅skill就係教weak form呀，linkage呀個啲</blockquote><br />\nching, ielts reading 9分，你個底都應該有反咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得份reading係考做唔做得切<br />\n有啲matching係要諗多幾層多過考英文（我考個份） <br />\n而我諗野算唔慢 所以呢份會有啲著數<br />\n但我英文一定唔係好 <br />\n都係個句睇同聽&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;講同寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb943ebfad0a7aedad3e689f88897cd9f55c39c3","tid":282844,"uid":121587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有學緊 最大感覺係同一間center但師資都可以爭好遠好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇你想學咩我先再講下個人經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發音？拼音？Grammar? Oral?</blockquote><br />\n我都想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Oral同拼音</blockquote><br />\n(我當幫手推下post俾其他有學嘅人入黎講其他經歷，我講到嘅只係我經歷個套，可能有bias唔好盡信）<br />\n<br />\n我係學IPA嘅 姐係查字典咪會見到呢啲<br />\n/rɪˈzʌlt/<br />\n頭個十堂就會係教呢啲代表乜<br />\n我上晒架啦，覺得最主要目標都係你查字典睇到呢個就知點樣最正確讀音，特別係有啲音係英文有但廣東話係無（呢啲你睇蕭叔叔channel都會有講），咁初頭就係執返正呢啲<br />\n<br />\n但都有好多人話上面呢啲phonetics差，主張學phonics，但邊樣好啲我諗真係好睇個人而我都唔熟，我剩係可以講多啲phonetics係咩如果你有野問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講緊咩學院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072931ac5c166df2d6848e5c40845fa352f331e6","tid":282844,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ted.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fted.com&d=%2F3W59dA5bV